## ğŸš€ About the Project

Bitcoin is highly volatile, and predicting its price accurately is both challenging and valuable.  
This project uses **machine learning models** â€” **XGBoost**, **SVM**, and **Logistic Regression** â€” to forecast Bitcoin price movements based on historical data. A web-based interface built with **Django** lets users easily interact with the models, upload data, and view results.

---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

| Tool/Technology        | Purpose                          |
|------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Python 3.7+            | Core programming language        |
| Scikit-learn           | Logistic Regression & SVM        |
| XGBoost                | Advanced gradient boosting       |
| Pandas / NumPy         | Data analysis & preprocessing    |
| Matplotlib / Seaborn   | Data visualization               |
| Django                 | Web-based user interface         |
| SQLite                 | Backend database                 |

