## âš™ï¸ Features

- âœ”ï¸ Predict price movement: **UP or DOWN**
- âœ”ï¸ View model comparison and accuracy
- âœ”ï¸ Upload CSV datasets through a web interface
- âœ”ï¸ Real-time evaluation with visual output
