---

## ğŸ“Š Model Performance

| Model               | Accuracy | Precision | Recall | F1-Score | RMSE  |
|---------------------|----------|-----------|--------|----------|--------|
| **XGBoost**         | 92%      | 91%       | 90%    | 90.5%    | 0.18   |
| **SVM**             | 85%      | 83%       | 82%    | 82.5%    | 0.26   |
| **Logistic Regression** | 81%  | 80%       | 78%    | 79%      | 0.30   |

